  "detailed_description": "<strong>Mutant Slimes, created to eat garbage waste in a mutant slime production laboratory called Slamus, got out of the control of scientists and began to eat people in the laboratory instead of garbage waste. A few scientists who managed to survive in the laboratory produced a new Slime to destroy these mutant slimes.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908840/extras/3f77394d9cc4bcf1bbcb3ca6db317666.poster.avif?t=1719497728\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908840/extras/3f77394d9cc4bcf1bbcb3ca6db317666.webm?t=1719497728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908840/extras/3f77394d9cc4bcf1bbcb3ca6db317666.mp4?t=1719497728\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You can carry 4 different weapons.<br></li><li>Weapon types are Pistol, SMG, Shotgun, Automatic Rifle, Minigun.<br></li><li>Destroy as many mutant slimes as you can while trying to survive waves lasting 20 to 90 seconds each.<br></li><li>Collect chemicals to get items from the store to further survive and destroy waves of enemies.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908840/extras/ab1bc89c432df24d48454318e36820a3.poster.avif?t=1719497728\" width=591 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2908840/extras/ab1bc89c432df24d48454318e36820a3.webm?t=1719497728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
